<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>RHOSYMEDRE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thisan lun, thisan lun,
 Kross chunga hung luong chun;
 Gitloh a ei tanin,
 Thiem ei chansak kittai;
 Migilo vawmpen thienna chuh,
 Kalvari thisan lun ahi,
 Kalvari thisan lun ahi.

[V2]
 2. Aw thisan, thisan lun,
 Thangvan dawngkawt nei hawn;
 Van gam nei tun tieng leh,
 Ka la tuoilo ding chuh;
 &quot;Thisan, thisan, thisan, thisan,&quot;
 Ti'n hailo in sa tang kau
 Ti'n hailo in sa tang kau.

[V3]
 3. Aw tang hawih Kalvari,
 Mite'n musit mahleu!
 Tang dang cheng cheng sangin,
 Ken ka ngaina pen hi;
 Aw nawpna tang, Aw mun thiengtho,
 Pathien Thisan a luonna chuh
 Pathien Thisan a luonna chuh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>99</hymn_number>
</song>